            bindings = <
                 &trans &trans              &mmv MOVE_UP     &trans          &mkp RCLK               &trans                &kp HOME         &trans           &trans   &kp END
                 &none  &mmv MOVE_LEFT      &mmv MOVE_DOWN   &mmv MOVE_RIGHT &mkp LCLK               &none                 &kp LEFT         &kp DOWN         &kp UP   &kp RIGHT
         &mo NUM &kp Q  &kp X               &kp M            &kp C           &kp V                   &none                 &msc SCRL_LEFT   &msc SCRL_DOWN &msc SCRL_UP &msc SCRL_RIGHT &none
