            bindings = <
                 &none  &none               &none            &none           &C_MUTE                 &KP_MULTIPLY          &kp N7           &kp N8           &kp N9   &KP_PLUS
              &C_VOL_DN &mmv MOVE_LEFT      &mmv MOVE_DOWN   &mmv MOVE_RIGHT &C_VOL_UP               &KP_DIVIDE            &kp N4           &kp N5           &kp N6   &KP_MINUS
